Property management software can make or break your operation at scale. We've watched operators lose entire weekends to manual rent reconciliation, miss critical maintenance windows, and hemorrhage money on vacancy days—all because they chose the wrong platform. After evaluating dozens of property management solutions and supporting operators managing everything from 20-unit apartment buildings to 5,000+ unit portfolios, our team has strong opinions on when Buildium beats AppFolio and vice versa.

This comparison cuts through the marketing noise. We're covering real pricing at scale, features that actually matter for day-to-day operations, and the gotchas that vendor demos never reveal.

